PrecisORDER PROHIBITING ENTRY ON CERTAIN LANDS IN THE YUKON TERRITORY (1998- No.2, LAPIERRE HOUSE HISTORIC SITE, Y.T.) - which prohibits, on a permanent basis, the staking of mineral claims or prospecting for precious minerals on approximately two hectares of land situated in the Yukon Territory.
